creator: Fitpet
descriptionHtml:
The easiest way to stay on top of your pet’s health

Understand your pet’s current health status in real-time using our at-home urinalysis kit, Ahead. It only takes a minute for a holistic urinalysis of over 10 parameters to detect and prevent potential diseases most commonly found in cats and dogs.

✔️ Internationally patented smartphone technology 
✔️ Real-time analysis
✔️ Detailed results
✔️ Track and manage your pet’s health

The Fitpet app must be used with Ahead, which can be purchased at Amazon.

For more information, please visit www.fitpetcorp.com
